text: Burton William Jenner (born September 6, 1978) is an American businessman. He is the owner of West LA Dogs. He is also a professional off-road racing driver. He is the oldest son of television personality and Olympic gold medalist Caitlyn Jenner and her first wife Chrystie Scott. ==Notes== ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:People from Malibu, California Category:Kardashian family Category:Businesspeople from Los Angeles Category:Jenner family
